WEBVTT

00:01.938 --> 00:04.000
Everyone wants a happy family life.


00:05.985 --> 00:08.153
Realistically, though, 


00:08.153 --> 00:09.571
even a husband and a wife 


00:09.572 --> 00:11.782
who truly love each other 


00:11.782 --> 00:14.000
will have some problems.


00:27.923 --> 00:29.800
You may wonder,


00:29.800 --> 00:33.000
‘What is the key to family happiness?’


00:36.682 --> 00:37.975
The Bible says: 


00:37.975 --> 00:40.102
“Happy are those hearing 


00:40.102 --> 00:43.000
the word of God and keeping it!”


00:44.648 --> 00:46.233
Would you like to know 


00:46.233 --> 00:48.651
how God’s Word, the Bible, 


00:48.652 --> 00:51.000
can help you have a happy family life?


00:54.115 --> 00:56.868
To find out, read the brochure 


00:56.868 --> 00:59.078
Your Family Can Be Happy. 


00:59.078 --> 01:02.666
You can download it free of charge 
from jw.org, 


01:02.667 --> 01:10.737
or you can obtain a copy 
from any of Jehovah’s Witnesses.

